OL,3,CRory McIlroy's home club celebrates
OL,4,Cback-to-back Masters champion
OL,6,FThere were scenes of jubilation at a
OL,7,FRory McIlroy's home golf club as he
OL,8,Fclaimed back-to-back Masters titles.
OL,10,FMcIlroy's hometown Holywood Golf Club
OL,11,Fin Co Down, Northern Ireland erupted
OL,12,Fin cheers as he tapped in a putt to
OL,13,Fwin by one on 12-under-par at Augusta
OL,14,FNational.
OL,16,FThe 36-year-old became the fourth man
OL,17,Fto win consecutives Masters titles,
OL,18,Fhaving first secured the green jacket
OL,19,F` and career grand slam ` last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
