OL,3,CRory McIlroy's home club celebrates
OL,4,Cback-to-back Masters champion
OL,6,FJoining Sir Nick Faldo with six major
OL,7,Fwins, McIlroy did not make it easy on
OL,8,Fhimself ` or fans who were at times
OL,9,Fleft with their heads in their hands.
OL,11,FThose watching on were well used to
OL,12,Fthe nerve-wracking rollercoaster of
OL,13,Femotions that comes with supporting
OL,14,Fthe Co Down man.
OL,16,FTables filled up early in the night,
OL,17,Ffollowing a Sunday roast, with around
OL,18,F150 people cheering on the hometown
OL,19,Fhero.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
