OL,3,CRory McIlroy's home club celebrates
OL,4,Cback-to-back Masters champion
OL,6,FAfter kissing his wife Erica, he
OL,7,Fembraced his parents Rosie and Gerry.
OL,9,FThere were cheers and hugs as fans
OL,10,Frose to their feet when McIlroy
OL,11,Ffinally secured a second green jacket,
OL,12,Finspiring the next generation who hope
OL,13,Fto follow in his footsteps.
OL,15,FSullivan Upper School, where McIlroy
OL,16,Fstudied, was represented among those
OL,17,Fcheering on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
