OL,3,CRory McIlroy's home club celebrates
OL,4,Cback-to-back Masters champion
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Press Association at
OL,7,FHolywood Golf Club, 19-year-old Zach
OL,8,FWoods said he and his friends thought
OL,9,Fthe victory was "really inspiring".
OL,11,FHe said: "It is great to be honest, to
OL,12,Fsee a boy from our community achieve
OL,13,Fsuch great things.
OL,15,F"It pushes us to strive to do the best
OL,16,Fthat we can to achieve the things that
OL,17,Fwe love."
