OL,3,CRory McIlroy's home club celebrates
OL,4,Cback-to-back Masters champion
OL,6,FHamish Johnson, 18, said he "never
OL,7,Fdoubted" McIlroy, adding: "He's got
OL,8,Fthe potential to be the best ever."
OL,10,FCelebrating the win, Leah James told
OL,11,Fthe Press Association "it was just
OL,12,Ffantastic" to watch along at Holywood
OL,13,F` having had to sneakily try and keep
OL,14,Fup with the action while on night
OL,15,Fshift last year.
OL,17,FMs James, from Bangor and a member at
OL,18,FHolywood, said McIlroy brought a lot
OL,19,Fof interest to the club.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@HO]oD@[OUpD@cO]sD@WOUtD@JO]
